---
/**
 * ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
 *  Contact.astro — CTA de contacto "¿Nos tomamos un café?"
 * ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════
 */
---

<section id="contacto" class="relative z-10 py-24" aria-label="Contacto">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div
      class="glass gradient-border relative overflow-hidden rounded-3xl p-10 text-center md:p-16"
      data-animate
    >
      <!-- Glow decorativo interior -->
      <div
        class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 opacity-20"
        aria-hidden="true"
        style="background: radial-gradient(ellipse at center, rgba(0,119,182,0.15) 0%, transparent 70%);"
      >
      </div>

      <!-- Emoji -->
      <div class="relative mb-6 text-5xl md:text-6xl" aria-hidden="true">
        ☕
      </div>

      <!-- Copy -->
      <h2
        class="relative mb-4 text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl"
      >
        ¿Nos tomamos <span class="gradient-text">un café</span>?
      </h2>
      <p
        class="relative mx-auto mb-8 max-w-xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-text-secondary"
      >
        Cuéntanos tu idea mientras disfrutamos de un buen café gaditano. Sin
        compromisos, sin letra pequeña. Solo una conversación sobre cómo hacer
        crecer tu negocio.
      </p>

      <!-- CTAs de contacto -->
      <div
        class="relative flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-4 sm:flex-row"
      >
        <a
          href="mailto:info@gadev.es"
          id="cta-contact-email"
          class="group inline-flex items-center gap-2 overflow-hidden rounded-full px-8 py-4 text-base font-semibold text-white transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105 hover:shadow-lg hover:shadow-cadiz-ocean/25"
          style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0077b6, #0096c7, #ee9b00);"
        >
          <svg
            class="h-5 w-5"
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
          >
            <rect width="20" height="16" x="2" y="4" rx="2"></rect>
            <path d="m22 7-8.97 5.7a1.94 1.94 0 0 1-2.06 0L2 7"></path>
          </svg>
          <span>info@gadev.es</span>
        </a>
        <a
          href="https://wa.me/34601443116"
          id="cta-contact-whatsapp"
          class="glass gradient-border inline-flex items-center gap-2 rounded-full px-8 py-4 text-base font-semibold text-text-primary transition-all duration-300 hover:scale-105"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener noreferrer"
        >
          <svg
            class="h-5 w-5"
            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
            fill="none"
            stroke="currentColor"
            stroke-width="2"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
          >
            <path
              d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07 19.5 19.5 0 0 1-6-6 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 4.11 2h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 .7 2.81 2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L8.09 9.91a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l1.27-1.27a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45 12.84 12.84 0 0 0 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 22 16.92z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
          <span>WhatsApp</span>
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Ubicación -->
      <p
        class="relative mt-8 flex items-center justify-center gap-2 text-sm text-text-muted"
      >
        <svg
          class="h-4 w-4"
          xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
          viewBox="0 0 24 24"
          fill="none"
          stroke="currentColor"
          stroke-width="2"
          stroke-linecap="round"
          stroke-linejoin="round"
        >
          <path
            d="M20 10c0 4.993-5.539 10.193-7.399 11.799a1 1 0 0 1-1.202 0C9.539 20.193 4 14.993 4 10a8 8 0 0 1 16 0"
          ></path>
          <circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"></circle>
        </svg>
        <span>Cádiz, España 🇪🇸</span>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
